44 previous or the current calendar year. A retailer that solely meets this
45 condition, or both this condition and the condition in subdivision (9) of this
46 subsection, is engaged in business on the first day of the first calendar month
47 occurring at least 60 days after the retailer's gross sales exceed the threshold."
